HEADWORD: Turban-top
<hw>Tur"ban-top`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Bot.)</fld>
<def>A kind of fungus with an irregularly wrinkled, somewhat globular
pileus (<spn>Helvella esculenta</spn> syn. <spn>Gyromitra
esculenta</spn>.).</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

